## Share [/share]

### Share [POST /share?destination_email={destination_email}&content_url={content_url}]

+ Parameters
    + destination_email (required, string) ... the recipient of the email
    + content_url (required, string) ... the URL to be sent via email

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "status": "OK"
            }
            
+ Response 400 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "status": "Bad Request. Either destination_email not valid or empty content_url"
